node.text: From antagonists to allies, Chloe and Nadine left their marks on the UNCHARTED series. Today, we celebrate the 4-year anniversary of their ultimate roles: protagonists in the epic standalone adventure, UNCHARTED: The Lost Legacy. Thank you to the fans for keeping the journey going!
